name: Boob Art 4
description: Abstract art with brown background. Splatter patterns and well......boob prints. Yes, I painted my boobs and stamped the canvas with them. These paintings are not meant to be pornographic in anyway, more of a novelty/collector's item (conversation starter?). I lost my mother in 2010 to breast cancer and wanted to do something to try to contribute to finding a cure. Somewhere in my brain this makes sense to me. I will be donating the money recieved from any sales to the Breast Cancer Foundation. 12in x 12in
